cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to an unknown enum 'nia9' will cause security negotiation failures during the initial setup phase, leading to NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting ul_frequencyBand to an invalid out-of-range value 999 will cause uplink frequency band misalignment, resulting in invalid carrier configurations and cell initialization errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ul_frequencyBand 設定為無效的超出範圍值 999 會導致上行頻率帶錯位，造成無效的載波配置和細胞初始化錯誤。
